      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Muddy Invitation",
        "Client": "Mud-caked Felyne",
        "Description": "Just look at me... Yuck! Covered\r\nfrom head to tail in mud. Meow\r\nI have to take a bath with Meowster...\r\nAnd you know Felynes hate baths!\r\nCan you go take care of that nasty\r\ncreature while I go scrub Meowster\u0027s\r\nback?",
        "Target": "Hunt an Almudron",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Une invitation boueuse",
        "Client": "Felyne boueux",
        "Description": "Chapristi, je suis recouvert de\r\nboue. J\u0027ai m\u00EAme d\u00FB prendre un\r\nbain, et je d\u00E9teste avoir le poil\r\nmouill\u00E9 ! Je compte sur toi\r\npour aller donner une bonne le\u00E7on\r\n\u00E0 ce miaonstre !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Un invito fangoso",
        "Client": "Felyne ricoperto di fango",
        "Description": "Guardami! Bleah, sono\r\nricoperto di fango. Miao, ora\r\ndevo fare il bagno col capo...\r\nE tu sai che noi Felyne odiamo\r\ni bagnetti. Puoi occuparti tu\r\ndi quel miaostriciattolo\r\nmentre io lavo il capo?",
        "Target": "Caccia un Almudron",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Eine schlammige Einladung",
        "Client": "Schlammverkrusteter Felyne",
        "Description": "Sieh mich nur an... B\u00E4h! Von Kopf bis\r\nSchwanz mit Schlamm bedeckt. Jetzt\r\nmuss ich mit dem Miauster baden...\r\nund wie du wei\u00DFt, hassen Felynen das!\r\nKannst du dich um die fiese Kreatur\r\nk\u00FCmmern, w\u00E4hrend ich dem Miauster\r\nden R\u00FCcken schrubbe?",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Almudron.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Invitaci\u00F3n embarrada",
        "Client": "Felyne enfangado",
        "Description": "Miau... Estoy totalmente\r\nenfangado. Me vi metido en la\r\ncaza de un Almudron y ahora\r\nsoy m\u00E1s una bola de cieno que\r\nde pelo. \u00BFPodr\u00EDa alguien\r\nencargarse de ese monstruo\r\nmientras me acicalo?",
        "Target": "Caza un Almudron",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0413\u0440\u044F\u0437\u043D\u044B\u0435 \u0434\u0435\u043B\u0430",
        "Client": "\u041A\u043E\u0442\u0442, \u0438\u0437\u043C\u0430\u0437\u0430\u043D\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u0433\u0440\u044F\u0437\u044C\u044E",
        "Description": "\u0422\u044B \u043F\u043E\u0441\u043C\u043E\u0442\u0440\u0438 \u043D\u0430 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F! \u0424\u0443!\r\n\u042F \u0432\u0435\u0441\u044C \u0432 \u0433\u0440\u044F\u0437\u0438 \u043E\u0442 \u0443\u0448\u0435\u0439 \u0434\u043E\r\n\u0445\u0432\u043E\u0441\u0442\u0430. \u041C\u043D\u0435 \u0442\u0435\u043F\u0435\u0440\u044C \u043D\u0430\u0434\u043E\r\n\u043F\u0440\u0438\u043D\u044F\u0442\u044C \u0432\u0430\u043D\u043D\u0443 \u2014 \u0430 \u0442\u044B \u0432\u0435\u0434\u044C\r\n\u0437\u043D\u0430\u0435\u0448\u044C, \u043A\u0430\u043A \u041A\u043E\u0442\u0442\u044B \u043D\u0435 \u043B\u044E\u0431\u044F\u0442\r\n\u043A\u0443\u043F\u0430\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F! \u041C\u043E\u0436\u0435\u0448\u044C \u0440\u0430\u0437\u043E\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F\r\n\u0441 \u0447\u0443\u0434\u043E\u0432\u0438\u0449\u0435\u043C, \u043F\u043E\u043A\u0430 \u044F \u043E\u0442\u043C\u043E\u043A\u0430\u044E?",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0410\u043B\u043C\u0443\u0434\u0440\u043E\u043D\u0430",
